# 🚗 Windshield Repair Jaipur

A simple and responsive website for windshield repair and replacement services in Jaipur.

---

## 🌟 Features

* Clean and modern UI
* Mobile-friendly design
* Click-to-call functionality 📞
* Service listing section
* Customer reviews section
* Call-to-action buttons

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3

---

## 📱 Key Functionality

* Users can directly call using:

  ```html
  <a href="tel:1234567890">Call Now</a>
  ```
* Works smoothly on mobile devices

---

## 📂 Project Structure

* index.html → Main webpage
* page.css → Styling (if used)

---

## 📍 Location

C-15 Jan Path, Nirman Nagar, Jaipur

---

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open `index.html` in any browser

---

